    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class manages the lifecycle of the Shaders. Source files are getting loaded via a StringFileReader and immediately compiled after loading. Any occupied memory for source-files and file-paths to the shader is being cleared once compilation succeeded and are not guaranteed to persist the compilation process. </para>
